title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2012 Apr 11 WE [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Wednesday, 11 April 2012


[sebaygo1]


Stefan Molyneux will be guest hosting today's show.

Today's guest is Chris Martenson, Duke University trained biochemist and publisher of The Crash Course video series, on why it's time to panic about Europe again, the implications of a QE3, and why everyone needs to freak out about "peak oil."
